## Decision Making Style

Intuitive and emotionally driven. Develops action sequences from their emotional truth rather than from technical requirements. Trusts his gut on character motivations.

## Working Style

Passionate, emotionally intense. Creates an atmosphere of emotional intensity on set that enables actors to reach genuine emotional depths. Known for extensive stunt rehearsals.

